ivardefs.name: action_
ivardefs.desc: The actions, if any, produced by the evaluation of the artifact.

ivardefs.name: author
ivardefs.desc: Provides a reference to the author of the request group.

ivardefs.name: authoredOn
ivardefs.desc: Indicates when the request group was created.

ivardefs.name: basedOn_
ivardefs.desc: A plan, proposal or order that is fulfilled in whole or in part by this request.

ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: A code that identifies what the overall request group is.

ivardefs.name: encounter
ivardefs.desc: Describes the context of the request group, if any.

ivardefs.name: groupIdentifier
ivardefs.desc: A shared identifier common to all requests that were authorized more or less simultaneously by a single author, representing the identifier of the requisition, prescription or similar form.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Allows a service to provide a unique, business identifier for the request.

ivardefs.name: instantiatesCanonical_
ivardefs.desc: A canonical URL referencing a FHIR-defined protocol, guideline, orderset or other definition that is adhered to in whole or in part by this request.

ivardefs.name: instantiatesUri_
ivardefs.desc: A URL referencing an externally defined protocol, guideline, orderset or other definition that is adhered to in whole or in part by this request.

ivardefs.name: intent
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the level of authority/intentionality associated with the request and where the request fits into the workflow chain.

ivardefs.name: note_
ivardefs.desc: Provides a mechanism to communicate additional information about the response.

ivardefs.name: priority
ivardefs.desc: Indicates how quickly the request should be addressed with respect to other requests.

ivardefs.name: reasonCode_
ivardefs.desc: Describes the reason for the request group in coded or textual form.

ivardefs.name: reasonReference_
ivardefs.desc: Indicates another resource whose existence justifies this request group.

ivardefs.name: replaces_
ivardefs.desc: Completed or terminated request(s) whose function is taken by this new request.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The current state of the request. For request groups, the status reflects the status of all the requests in the group.

ivardefs.name: subject
ivardefs.desc: The subject for which the request group was created.

properties.desc: A group of related requests that can be used to capture intended activities that have inter-dependencies such as "give this medication after that one".
